Items:
	•	Confirm thresholds for handwriting and low-quality scans.
	•	Finalize XML transformation ownership (upstream vs. downstream).
	•	Validate regulatory submission path (direct vs. intermediate).
	•	Define retraining cadence and drift monitoring approach.

Speaker Notes:

These are coordination items, not blockers.
Most dependencies relate to ownership and confidence thresholds, which can evolve alongside MVP testing.
None of these change the 2025 deliverable timeline — they fine-tune the 2026 refinement plan.

